          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " or Corvette Z06. While some might refer to that as legal theft, we’re wondering what everyone thinks of the 2022 Dodge Challenger Hellcat Redeye showed off recently by Cochise County Sheriff’s Office.",
